| image2    =Ceiling-Unlimited-1942.jpg
| alt2      =
| caption2  = Welles and Col. Arthur I. Ennis, head of the public relations branch of the [[United States Army Air Forces|Army Air Forces]], discuss plans for the [[CBS Radio]] series ''[[Ceiling Unlimited]]'' (October 1942).
<!-- Image 3 -->
| image3    = Welles-Draft-1943.jpg
| alt3      =
