<!-- Image 4 -->
| image4    = Mercury-Wonder-Show-Welles.jpg
| alt4      =
| caption4  = "Hello, suckers!" Orson the Magnificent welcomes the audience to ''[[The Mercury Wonder Show]]'' (August 1943).
